  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5109093/" class="title-link">美丽的数学</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5109093"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ziyam/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u50230066-12.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ziyam/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">猫儿觉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-09-26"
      class="main-meta">2011-09-26 17:08:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5109093_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是一部从听说就让我觉得兴奋的书。真正看到了这本书，真的很有魅力。先不说本身带着怎样无穷无尽的奇妙数学证明，但是很像笔记的书本身的设计就很让我喜欢。而书中各种证明的美妙，不是言语所能形容的，人类的智慧在对数学的探索上体现得最为完美！

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
